{"tid":2029884,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過唔知點解頭痛","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T17:15:52.000Z","uid":325029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4defee27c4324abbdf85744beb438f5a6aaa168d","tid":2029884,"uid":325029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"呢排成日都覺得好似頭重重<br />\n又唔係話頭好痛<br />\n但係就唔太舒服<br />\n<br />\n可能呢排瞓得麻麻嘅關係<br />\n成日間中醒咗<br />\n之後起身就覺得冇乜點瞓過<br />\n都持續咗有2,3個月<br />\n<br />\n頭痛又未去到要食止痛藥嗰地步<br />\n但成日都feel到頭重重<br />\n<br />\n真係救鬼命"},{"pid":"f004be61c13280fa699fe927f0cc95c878c349b0","tid":2029884,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"有無暈？"},{"pid":"fa1a80d058485df0b7197bcdf779b9d93ef32a9b","tid":2029884,"uid":325029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f004be61c13280fa699fe927f0cc95c878c349b0","tid":2029884,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"有無暈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"唔覺有"},{"pid":"d03745e518da3dc82cd877408e8f36c36e91794f","tid":2029884,"uid":275698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"應該話，冇人知點解頭痛"},{"pid":"0619acf81bafa8c86bcfe743eca15d39dc98c795","tid":2029884,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03745e518da3dc82cd877408e8f36c36e91794f","tid":2029884,"uid":275698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"應該話，冇人知點解頭痛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"顱內壓增加 可以係食得太多鹽引致"},{"pid":"a348facec81835a46e4a3dbc170d2a9cf1b2da54","tid":2029884,"uid":275698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0619acf81bafa8c86bcfe743eca15d39dc98c795","tid":2029884,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03745e518da3dc82cd877408e8f36c36e91794f","tid":2029884,"uid":275698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim